import axios from "axios"
let baseUrl = 'http://74.208.25.43:4000'
const url="http://localhost:3000/users"


export const getUsers= async()=>{
    return await axios.get(url);
}
export let login = () =>  baseUrl+'/api/v1/user/login'
export let signUp = () => baseUrl+'/api/v1/user/register'    
export let verifyOtp = () =>  baseUrl+'/api/v1/user/verify_otp'
export let addEvent = () =>  baseUrl+'/api/v1/event/createEvent'
export let timeZone = () =>  baseUrl+'/api/v1/timezone/list'
export let eventList = () =>  baseUrl+'/api/v1/event/eventList'
export let bookedEvent = () =>  baseUrl+'api/v1/event/bookedEvent'
export let viewEvent = () =>  baseUrl+'/api/v1/event/viewEvent'
